ygData.subject: Re: Guild
ygData.msgSnippet: Lion Knights is not bad, but will it mean more for warrior-like class, like Higher Order of Arcane guild related more to mages class?  Why not make it Supreme
ygData.messageBody:
Lion Knights is not bad, but will it mean more for warrior-like class, like
Higher Order of Arcane guild related more to mages class? Why not make it
"Supreme Order of Kiasu" (better than 'Higher', hehe), since pple can hunt
lion for the hide and make armor? Wait pple say simi lion guild, I slain
ya lion skin and make armor, then we die cock stand liao, hehe. Further
more, foreigner might even think 'Kiasu' is a fantasy name but yet local
kakis can identify us as an local guild easily. ;)
